this is one of many controllers that administrates the pods inside a kurnetes cluster. its function is to always ensure that the application will have the exact same amount of pod replicas in the beggining of the the application will be running in the present time.

example: i have a replicaset of 3 replicas with the pod template in the start of my cluster, the ReplicaSet will make 3 pods to run at the same time always 